 ost-)socialist transformation and memory studies\, as well as public sphe
 re and media change\, with a further focus on international communication
 . She has conducted research on topics such as journalistic practices\, m
 edia use\, and digital literacy in Sub-Saharan Africa and the Middle East
 . Her work integrates qualitative and quantitative methods within compara
 tive research designs\, frequently carried out in the context of European
  collaborative projects. Her current research examines the interplay betw
