  I and the Russian Revolution as his loyalty to his wife\, Tonya (Geraldi
 ne Chaplin)\, collides with his ardent bond with Lara (Julie Christie). T
 he film won five Academy Awards\, including Cinematography and Score\, an
 d five Golden Globes\, including Best Motion Picture - Drama and Best Dir
 ector. [197 min\; drama\; English]</p>
